{"word":"G5271 - ὑποκρίνομαι - hypokrínomai - hoop-ok-rin'-om-ahee - Feign","slug":"G5271","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑποκρίνομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hypokrínomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hoop-ok-rin'-om-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Feign"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C5;&#x0314;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03BA;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - hupokrinomai</b> - <i>hoop-ok-rin'-om-ahee</i><p/>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>; to <i>decide</i> (<i>speak</i> or <i>act</i>) <i>under</i> a false part, that is, (figuratively) <i>dissemble</i> (<i>pretend</i>): - feign."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4942\">G4942</a>, <a href=\"#/G505\">G505</a>, <a href=\"#/G5272\">G5272</a>, <a href=\"#/G5273\">G5273</a>"}]}